one million = ur milion.
one billion = ur bilion.
one trillion = un trilion.
one quadrillion = ur pevarilion.
one quintillion = ur pemilion.
one sextillion = ur c'hwec'hilion.
one septillion = ur seizhilion.
one octillion = un eizhilion.
one nonillion = un navilion.
one decillion = un dekilion.
...

one mi-lliard = ur miliard.
one bi-lliard  = ur biliard.
one tri-lliard = un triliard.
one quadri-lliard = ur pevariliard.
one quinti-lliard = ur pemiliard.
one sexti-lliard = ur c'hwec'hiliard.
one septi-lliard = ur seizhiliard.
one octi-lliard = un eizhiliard.
one noni-lliard = un naviliard.
one deci-lliard = un dekiliard.
...
